1
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:10,800
Xiao Jingyan,

2
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:14,320
I, Yan Qingshu, must marry you today.

3
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,320
Cui Tingru,

4
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:20,360
You moved troops without authorization and imprisoned the Crown Prince,

5
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:21,720
bringing chaos to the court.

6
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,560
Do you know

7
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,120
this is an unforgivable crime?

8
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,640
What I have done

9
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,120
is all for the state.

10
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:32,640
The Fourth Prince is far superior to the Crown Prince in civil and military affairs.

11
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:35,280
With the late emperor's edict to legitimize him,

12
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,759
I am merely following the will of the people.

13
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,300
Following the mandate of heaven.

14
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,520
But it is you, Heir Xiao,

15
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,160
bringing troops without an edict,

16
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:46,880
trespassing into Taihe Hall and plotting rebellion.

17
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:50,680
Who is the one committing an unpardonable crime?

18
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,780
Following the people's will indeed.

19
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,680
You hold the crown prince hostage to command the officials,

20
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,680
and disregard the laws of the state.

21
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,840
If you do not submit to execution today,

22
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:03,100
under the iron hooves of my Xuanjia Army,

23
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,740
there will be no place for traitors to stand.

24
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,479
Prince Xiao,

25
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,480
you might as well try.

26
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,040
Let's see if my blood spills first,

27
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:17,520
or the Crown Prince's head falls first.

28
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,240
In the third year of Changhe,

29
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:23,130
Prince Ling secretly sold refined iron to Beidi,

30
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,970
making millions in profit.

31
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,760
In the fifth year of Changhe,

32
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:30,040
Prince Ling embezzled the northern border's military rations,

33
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:33,400
causing 2,000 soldiers to die at the border.

34
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,450
In the 14th year of Changhe,

35
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:39,200
Prince Ling even used rotten armor and blunt swords as military supplies,

36
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:42,680
leading to the total annihilation of the 3,000 Zhenbei Army.

37
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,520
A mere woman,

38
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:51,720
how dare you speak nonsense about state affairs in Taihe Hall?

39
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:52,400
Guards!

40
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,040
Drag her out!

41
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:56,280
I am Yan Qingshu, daughter of the Duke.

42
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:59,200
Today was supposed to be my wedding day.

43
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,280
But before drinking the nuptial wine,

44
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,920
I came to rid the Emperor of evil ministers and rectify the court.

45
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:06,980
Lady Yan, barging into the hall in your red bridal gown,

46
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:09,080
you certainly have courage.

47
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,240
The Records of the Officials are right here.

48
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,720
They detail all the court's dark secrets and factional struggles.

49
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:17,120
Would the Prince of Ling like to take a look?

50
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,240
The Records of the Officials are just a rumor.

51
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,000
No such thing exists in this world.

52
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,640
How dare you forge a book to deceive the public?

53
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:27,920
The Records of the Officials is a secret record from the late Emperor.

54
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:30,180
It contains the royal family's secrets,

55
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,680
the officials' corrupt deeds,

56
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,600
bribery, factionalism, and conspiracies.

57
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:36,160
Time, place, witnesses, details.

58
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,520
Grand Secretary Zhou Xiangquan

59
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:42,400
privately occupied silver mines and embezzled ten thousand taels of silver.

60
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,329
Vice Minister of Rites Wu Mingtang

61
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:47,240
played with catamites and sold official titles.

62
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,160
The Third Prince colluded with Southern border witchcraft

63
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,720
to curse the Eastern Palace.

64
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:55,050
The Fourth Prince and Prince Ling colluded with Northern Di

65
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,520
to commit treason.

66
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,480
For all these matters, the time and places are detailed,

67
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:02,740
and both witnesses and physical evidence can be verified.

68
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,880
This is no record of deeds.

69
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,500
It is clearly a book of life and death.

70
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,240
Your Highness, Prince Ling.

71
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:17,760
You instigated the princes, illegally forged weapons,

72
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:20,760
poisoned the Emperor, secretly colluded with Beidi,

73
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,200
slaughtered the loyal, and trampled on the innocent.

74
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,840
Did you think you could hide these crimes

75
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,100
and keep them in the dark forever?

76
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,840
Every single deed here,

77
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,760
every single one of them,

78
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,680
is your death warrant.

79
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,920
Brother.

80
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,620
Royal brother.

81
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:57,800
What a masterful play of checks and balances.

82
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,960
I concede defeat

83
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,680
wholeheartedly.

84
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,330
Black Armor Guards, listen to my command.

85
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,200
Put down your weapons.

86
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,600
You...

87
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:22,960
Xiao Jingyan,

88
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:26,360
who allowed you to write a letter to break off the engagement?

89
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:26,920
I...

90
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,580
Who allowed you to go to your death alone?

91
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:34,040
From now on, you are not allowed to leave me behind.

92
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:36,480
Otherwise, I, Yan Qingshu, swear to heaven

93
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,940
that I will never forgive you in all my lives.

94
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,300
I was wrong.

95
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,280
Qingshu,

96
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:47,680
How about

97
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,820
we use this hall as our wedding venue?

98
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,600
With heaven and earth as witnesses,

99
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,530
I, Xiao Jingyan,

100
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:59,100
wish to take you, Yan Qingshu, as my wife.

101
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,760
You are the only one in this life.

102
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,370
I promise you peace for the rest of my life,

103
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:08,120
and pledge you eternity till our hair turns white.

104
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,660
Never leaving in poverty,

105
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,890
never abandoning in life or death.

106
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,370
This heart and this body

107
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,410
will forever belong to you.

108
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,360
You're awake.

109
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,480
Jingyan,

110
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,600
I just had a dream.

111
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:13,440
I dreamt of Father, Mother, Xiaotao,

112
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,120
and Sanniang.

113
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,920
They were all alive and well.

114
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,160
Did you

115
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:22,760
dream of me?

116
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,000
I did.

117
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,080
I dreamt

118
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,200
that we held hands,

119
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:34,610
braved the wind and snow together,

120
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,659
and explored the world together.

121
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:41,840
Jingyan...

122
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,920
Promise me one thing.

123
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:45,880
Okay.

124
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,960
I will promise you anything.

125
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,240
I want you

126
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,600
to live well.

127
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,600
To live a long life.

128
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:03,480
To see peace all over the world

129
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:06,240
and people living in peace.

130
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:10,400
I don't want you to be sad for me.

131
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,800
I won't leave.

132
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,520
I'm just using another way

133
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,280
to stay by your side.

134
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:25,240
I will turn into wind and snow,

135
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:30,720
mountains and rivers,

136
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,800
and everything around you.

137
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,080
Whenever you miss me,

138
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,760
just whisper to me.

139
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,760
I will definitely hear it.

140
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:47,920
Okay.

141
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,920
I promise you.

142
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,720
Qingshu.

143
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,000
Qingshu.

144
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,080
Qingshu.

145
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:37,240
Qing...

146
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,960
What is recorded in this file

147
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,280
are hidden sins

148
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,160
and transgressions.

149
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,020
It is the murky current hidden

150
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,960
beneath the court robes and jade belts.

151
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,680
Presenting it to the Supreme Court today

152
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,800
is not for personal revenge,

153
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,600
nor to eliminate political opponents.

154
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:12,660
We only hope you all

155
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,160
use the law as your ruler,

156
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:17,080
use moral principles as your compass,

157
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,920
and rectify yourselves.

158
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,120
Then rectify others.

159
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:22,360
Let the whole nation know reverence and keep boundaries,

160
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,160
and restore peace to the world.

161
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,560
The Records of the Hundred Officials acts as a mirror,

162
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,480
reflecting the good and evil in people's hearts.

163
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,160
As a sword,

164
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,760
it slays the treacherous and wicked.

165
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,200
But it should never

166
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:36,120
become a weapon in anyone's hands to manipulate life and death,

167
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,180
and eliminate political opponents.

168
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,200
Water.

169
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:47,960
From today on,

170
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,200
all cases under the Dali Court's jurisdiction

171
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,680
must be handled fairly and impartially.

172
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:55,440
We will take the law as the standard and the people as our priority.

173
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,080
We will use these records to wash away corruption,

174
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,440
purify the realm,

175
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:02,920
and restore noble justice to the world.

176
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:08,280
Lord Wang.

177
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:11,160
The Cangzhou military pay case three years ago,

178
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:12,880
Beneath the Qingzhou Residence,

179
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:14,880
you buried 200,000 taels of silver.

180
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:15,720
Is this true?

181
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,280
Take him down.

182
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,000
Lord Zhang.

183
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,880
Lady Liu, whom you kept in your outer residence,

184
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,920
once held your infant daughter

185
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:24,240
and knelt before your gates for 3 days and nights,

186
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:26,600
begging you to acknowledge your blood and spare them.

187
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,760
Yet you gave the mother and daughter a packet of arsenic.

188
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:31,420
And your wife bestowed them 3 feet of white silk.

189
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,280
Is this true?

190
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,560
In the autumn examination of the 11th year of Changhe,

191
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,960
Lord Zhou illegally sold 7 candidate quotas.

192
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,760
Perverting the law and disgracing the scholars.

193
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:39,640
Take him away.

194
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,760
Qingshu.

195
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:30,120
I am heading to the frontier thousands of miles away,

196
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:33,050
to protect our picturesque lands and all our people.

197
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:37,400
When peace is restored and the country is stable,

198
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,860
I will step into every spring breeze,

199
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,840
every winter snow,

200
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:46,860
and every blooming flower bed where you once lingered,

201
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:50,810
to express all my yearning for the rest of my life,

202
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,890
telling you everything one by one.

203
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,360
Cuimei.

204
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:31,960
Cuimei.

205
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,600
Yong.

206
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:35,640
Huachao.

207
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:35,640
Kun.

208
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:36,640
Weikun, Huachao.

209
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:39,840
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

210
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:43,720
Shuang, Bin.

211
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:44,200
Shuang.

212
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,160
Ningzheng.

213
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:48,760
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

214
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,000
Weichao.

215
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:53,600
Wei, Chao.

216
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,170
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

217
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:13,760
Xi.

218
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,720
Tao, Qiang.

219
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,800
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

220
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,000
Yiyi.

221
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:28,960
Si, Si, Si.
